            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"從查理一世到特朗普 徵稅權的歷史警示\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4v9L_cn13J0ABEuCyhe9ZA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/82c34910-0f2c-11f1-bfef-0b81a12bebb4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">從查理一世到特朗普 徵稅權的歷史警示</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
