        {
            "title": "網絡安全軟件類股票大跌 Anthropic在Claude AI模型中引入安全工具",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FR31Ta0ydNgvqwmUILUUIA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/55a0e6c5759355c81cd01567123d51fc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 網絡安全軟件類股周五大跌，此前Anthropic PBC在其Claude AI模型中引入一項新的安全功能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Crowdstrike Holdings跌幅居前，下跌8%，Cloudflare Inc.下跌8.1%。與此同時，Zscaler下跌5.5%，SailPoint下跌9.4%，Okta Inc.下跌9.2%。全球X網絡安全ETF下跌4.9%，收於2023年11月以來的最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic表示，新工具「掃描代碼庫中的安全漏洞，並建議針對性的軟件補丁供人工審核。」該公司表示，目前該更新僅提供有限的研究預覽版。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-397c931c-286b-34db-8397-24d6b7664b7e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Usfn.27GQre7R35arRVyvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9c2ec311d43eb6ceb611da88a621e6d8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">網絡安全股的下跌是AI競爭擔憂引發的軟件股拋售的又一例證。這種焦慮情緒已持續數周，iShares 擴展科技-軟件部門ETF今年以來已下跌超過 23%，勢將創下2008年金融危機以來最大的季度跌幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「對軟件股的拋售一直在穩步持續，今天安全軟件股又因為一條新聞而出現了小範圍的拋售，」Triple D Trading的首席交易員Dennis Dick表示。「這種市場對投資者來說很可怕，因為一旦出現任何動盪跡象，價格就會持續下跌。保持謹慎是理所當然的，因為之前有人認為軟件股下跌過度了，但它卻還在繼續下跌。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拋售很大程度上是因為Anthropic、OpenAI和Alphabet等公司發布的新AI工具，投資者擔心「氛圍式編程」（即由AI自動生成、修改和調試代碼）的能力將使用戶能夠創建自己的應用程式，從而減少對傳統產品的需求，並對相關公司的成長、利潤率和定價能力造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Cyber Stocks Slide as Anthropic Unveils Claude Security Tool (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
